					<p>This is a retelling of the Goldilocks story, where all of the characters have been transformed into science fiction style equivalents. </p>
<p>I thought this was clever and very amusing. I loved the line, &#8220;Found a bit of a funny&#8221; <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> The frame is very light hearted, especially with lines like, &#8220;Yours in exploration.&#8221; Which reminds me: Captain H made me think of this:<br />
