				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thanks all &#8211; glad you liked it &#8211; giggles are always acceptable.</p>
<p>Regarding the framing text:<br />
Originally I had a more serious techno-babble going on in the framing as well but I changed it because:<br />
a) I couldn&#8217;t get the length short enough that way &#8211; technobabbly doesn;t communicate so well.<br />
b) I thought it needed to be lighter to be amusing.</p>
<p>When I published it (and still now) I felt quite conflicted about the frame text. Will have to think carefully about a rewrite.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

